## Custom fields [/customFields]

### /getCustomFields.php [POST /getCustomFields.php]

Get all custom fields for one object type.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes (object)
        + for: `company` (enum[string], required) - type of the object
            + Members
                + company
                + contact
                + sale
                + project
                + invoice
                + ticket
                + milestone
                + todo
                + meeting

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (array)
        + (object)
            + id: 1 (number)
            + for: contact (enum[string])
                + Members
                    + company
                    + contact
                    + sale
                    + project
                    + invoice
                    + ticket
                    + milestone
                    + todo
                    + meeting
            + name: custom field name (string)
            + type: date (enum[string])
                + Members
                    + date
                    + string
                    + int
                    + money
                    + boolean
                    + alt_email
                    + enum
                    + textblob
                    + set
                    + company
                    + contact
                    + employee
                    + auto_calculated_field
                    + telephone
                    + product
                    + number
                    + url
                    + auto_increment
            + group: extra information (string)

