### /addCustomFieldOption.php [POST /addCustomFieldOption.php]

Adding options to a custom field (for set and enum type custom fields).

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes (object)
        + custom_field_id: 1 (number, required) - ID of the custom field
        + option_name: option 5 (string, required) - name of the option
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            127 (number) - ID of the custom field option
        }
